{"tid":1734722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅隧攻入理大，係救到人定係送頭?","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T13:41:44.000Z","uid":37971,"like":140,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c535062bcafcb15ba1bffdd49595ff3ac18499","tid":1734722,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"首先講明<br />\n手足無論有乜嘢決定，我都唔會割席<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>港島人吹雞！由港島攻入紅磡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734514\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734514</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要知道一入去紅隧，一係向前走一係向後走，兩邊各一個出口<br />\n九龍出口就已經重狗<br />\n港島入去，如果港島入口畀狗包抄<br />\n點走? <br />\n尖沙咀去到旺角一帶已經有手足幫緊手<br />\n點救? 仲夠唔夠人救?<br />\n咁樣分分鐘係玩緊班手足<br />\n手足畀狗咬一個就少一個<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗清楚，呢個策略係咪一個明智之舉<br />\nanyway<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆都唔割！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc681609f9c22404cd2c8b97fba8d96efa10cf94","tid":1734722,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"81eccb58081acf070bbfdbbfb95b48246d004ff7","tid":1734722,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:07.000Z","msg":"重要呀！"},{"pid":"1bce61204a8f4afdcd9e8963cc213afaa149f61b","tid":1734722,"uid":37971,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"我唔想有手足再送頭&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ce89af5dcea2baff7cbcdb75bc10685a9fa88db1","tid":1734722,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"唔該大家"},{"pid":"4abdd50df2483ef4b675e153cc12ff9cef528186","tid":1734722,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5246c43608f360fb032c61f0cd944a2b91800340","tid":1734722,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"